  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objectives of the consultancy are to:
- Provide external quality assurance of the Rio-markers and the environment marker
assigned to the 2019 commitments to be reported to OECD DAC CRS and make
recommendations for possible corrections before final submission to DAC.
- Prepare an overview report of Danish &#x201C;green&#x201D; development finance in 2019,
including support targeting the three Rio conventions and in support of
environment.
- Assist MFA in drafting the Danish input to upcoming national MMR report to
EU in climate relevant financing in accordance with relevant reporting guidelines
and formats.</narrative>
